<collectingCountry box="[252,344,1754,1779]" name="Bahamas" pageId="262" pageNumber="263">Bahama</collectingCountry>
Is. The 
<typeStatus box="[436,484,1755,1778]" pageId="262" pageNumber="263">type</typeStatus>
